casebody.data:
MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

99-1803. Dollar Bank FSB v. Cuyahoga Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, Nos. 97-G-29 and 97-G-8. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
